<br>
Glamour of Kintaz has had its mana cost lowered from 275 to 125.<br>
Demi Lich has been lowered to a Level 56 spell from Level 60. <br>
Arch Lich has been improved to a 35 Mana for 53 Hitpoint conversion. The previous ratio was 20 mana for 31 hitpoints. <br>
Quivering Veil of Xarn has been altered. It no longer has a damage shield component and now heals 150 hitpoints instantly instead of over 4 ticks.<br>
New Cleric Res spells lower, and pushing the xp regained to lower levels (also added lower level res to paladins)<br>
Evacuate/Succor lowered in mana cost.<br>
Lower level evacuate/Succor spells added.<br>
<br>
Let's keep track of what's done, what levels, what changes, what kinds of work. At least if we know what's being done we can make suggestions and give Verant some input. So far it looks like they are putting some real thought into the high level spells to see what could be changed, going over them carefully to see if they are well-built instead of assuming it's all fine. That's encouraging to see. <br>
<br>
As much as possible lets try to keep this to updates and information, rather than opinion on what's been done.  Suggestions for Verant might be useful as well, although I have my doubts if they read this forum. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufilanfyretracker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Filan Fyretracker</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/12/02 7:52:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Caster Balance Changes</span><hr size=1> one thing id like to see is spreading of spell drops in luclin for lvl 60 nukes from the current 1 mob only system. <p><center><a href="mailto:filan@snet.net"><img SRC="http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/filansig3.jpg" height=172 width=444 border="0"></a>
