actual emergency, do you really think we'd stick around to tell you?</i></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.kestrelarts.com/images/grimicon.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>(Title left blank)</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/12/02 9:24:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=681.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> From Whizbang's link</span><hr size=1> Memory Blur spells changed: <br>
