<br>
In relation to other casters I think Wizards are balanced fine, if not the best of the 4.  Except in the aspect of PvP, I mean could Verant make necro's any cheaper?<br>
<br>
In relation of Casters vs Melee, we are underbalanced as a whole.  And personally I think they need to adjust the Damage output of all casters over all.  While still maintaining the balance of the casters (not an easy job).<br>
<br>
Wizards should be able to sustain Monk level damage for 4-7 minutes or so.  Now after 20 to 30 minutes I would expect on a normal encounter for Monks and Rogues to do more then Wizards.  Just because that is the advantage of a melee. <br>
<br>
But on very short term battles, such as under 4-5 minutes, then I would expect Wizards to Outdamage Monks and Rogues.  Cause that is what *wizards* are designed for.  Doing the most damage in the shortest amount of time.  <br>
<br>
And if we could do 10k damage in 20 seconds on kunark mob that would be fine.  With mobs having 200k, 500k, and possibly 1000k hp.  We need to be able to do massive damage in 4-5 minutes to maintain that aspect of doing the most damage in the shortest amount of time.  Doing 20k damage in the first 2 minutes is not really comparable to a mob with 300k hp.  <br>
<br>
Now with the latest additions of Mana regen, such as C3, FT, familiars, Potg, Mod Rod 2, etc etc.  We can get massive manaregen and do larger amounts of damage over battles.  And there are certain battles in Luclin where it has been proven that Wizards are an essential part of the encounter.  Doing massive damage.  <br>
<br>
In Armok's study it shows how far a wizard falls behind melee in damage as time goes on.  Which this is to be expected for the most part.  The real problem is currently it happens very fast to start.  Even with Mass regen, it's hard to outdamage them due to Aggro.<br>
<br>
The best thing they could do is just look over our basic damage spells that are used on a regular basis and rebalance them to balance our concept of casters with the melee.  <br>
<br>
Although with extended battle times this just adds a whole new equation to melee vs caster damage. <br>
<br>
